    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a dedicated project car or a comprehensive source for parts. The body shows significant signs of age, including heavy rust on the lower panels and several noticeable dents. Mechanically, it requires substantial work to be roadworthy again, as the engine runs roughly and the transmission is slipping. The interior is heavily worn with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is priced to reflect these extensive needs.",
