    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving exactly as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. With its flawless exterior and a pristine interior that still feels brand new, this is a rare find for any discerning driver looking for top-tier quality and reliability.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a major restoration project or a donor vehicle for parts. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy rust on the wheel arches and rocker panels, along with several deep scratches and a large dent on the passenger side door. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and the transmission is currently slipping significantly. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a non-functional climate control system. It will need to be towed from its current location, as it is not presently roadworthy.",
      "price": 4500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive excellence, maintained to a high standard. This vehicle offers a refined driving experience, characterized by its reliable performance and a well-preserved interior that speaks to its careful stewardship. Every component reflects a commitment to quality, ensuring this remains a sophisticated choice for the professional driver. We invite you to experience its superior handling and timeless aesthetic firsthand.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! This beauty has been such a joy to own and is still running like a champ. It's been well-loved and is in really solid shape, making it the perfect reliable ride for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. I've taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll feel the love the moment you get behind the wheel. It's ready for a new home and plenty more adventures\u2014come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, managed by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014critical for chassis rigidity. The suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution translates to precise turn-in. While showing honest patina consistent with its mileage, the internal combustion health and drivetrain synchronization are exceptional for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Minor exterior wear. Runs smooth. No mechanical issues.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly well-cared-for vehicle that strikes an excellent balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for its age but otherwise very clean. Inside, the cabin is a highlight; the charcoal leather seats are supple with no rips or tears, and the dual-zone climate control and premium infotainment system work perfectly. Mechanically, this car is sound, featuring a responsive engine that has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new brake pads, and a battery replacement. The tires show plenty of life on the original 18-inch alloy wheels. It drives straight, shifts smoothly, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a solid, honest example for a buyer looking for reliability without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 34850.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained vehicle that balances performance with exceptional value. This unit has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical reliability and aesthetic appeal. Featuring a clean history and consistent maintenance records, it represents an ideal acquisition for the discerning driver seeking quality without the premium of a showroom-new price tag. Experience a refined driving experience in a vehicle that remains in commendable condition throughout.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    }
  ],
